            <h1> Some of Copenhagen’s best cheap eats - for students by students </h1>
            <h2> WHAT IS MealOnSU.dk </h2>
            <p>
                MealOnSU.dk is your go-to website when it comes to finding affordable, high quality restaurants and cafés in Copenhagen. It can be difficult as a student to find delicious food for a fair price. Our goal is to give you the best options when it comes to finding low-cost meals on a student budget.
